<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227594>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Live specimens of third-stage praniza larvae: A and B, Gnathia albipalpebrata n. sp.; C and D, Gnathia parvirostrata n. sp.; E and F, Gnathia dejimagi n. sp. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227583>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Gnathia albipalpebrata n. sp., holotype, male adult (NSMT Cr- 22965, total length, 10.0 mm): A, body, dorsal view; B, frontal border with mandibles and eye, dorsal view (broken line shows mediofrontal process of paratype, NSMT Cr- 22966); C, head, lateral view; D, pleotelson, dorsal view; E, right antennula; F, right antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227583/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227584>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gnathia albipalpebrata n. sp., holotype, male adult (NSMT Cr- 22965, total length, 10.0 mm): A, left maxilliped, ventral view; B, right pylopod, ventral view; C, right pereopod 2, lateral view; D, right pleopod 2, ventral view; E, penes, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227585>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Gnathia albipalpebrata n. sp., paratype, female adult (NSMT Cr- 22966, total length, 7.8 mm): A, body, dorsal view; B, frontal border, dorsal view; C, pleotelson, dorsal view. P 1 = pereonite 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227585/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227586>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gnathia albipalpebrata n. sp., paratype, third-stage larva (NSMT Cr- 33966, total length, 8.4 mm); A, body, dorsal view; B, head, dorsal view; C, pleotelson, dorsal view; D, right antennula; E, left antenna; F, mandible; G, paragnath; H, maxillula; I, maxilliped; J, pereopod 1; K, left pereopod 2; L, left pleopod 2. En = endite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227586/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

